249
00:20:27,551 --> 00:20:31,711
Princess Runing was honored and distinguished.

250
00:20:31,711 --> 00:20:36,711
But someone changed the pattern of her clothes,

251
00:20:36,711 --> 00:20:39,711
and she was accused of treason...

252
00:20:40,511 --> 00:20:43,271
and ended up as she is now.

253
00:20:45,431 --> 00:20:48,751
So, Princess Runing

254
00:20:48,751 --> 00:20:52,151
was also framed by you?

255
00:20:52,151 --> 00:20:56,411
How could I have succeeded so easily had you not been paranoid?

256
00:20:56,411 --> 00:20:58,331
It's all your fault.

257
00:20:58,331 --> 00:21:02,511
You are the greatest threat to my clan.

258
00:21:02,511 --> 00:21:07,911
As a descendant of the Xiao family, I shall right the wrongs for Great Cang.

259
00:21:07,911 --> 00:21:11,431
The throne is rightfully mine.

260
00:21:11,431 --> 00:21:14,351
I am the rightful heir to the throne.

261
00:21:14,351 --> 00:21:16,831
But you are not the son of the late emperor.

262
00:21:16,831 --> 00:21:21,671
You are the son of Consort Shu and her lover.

263
00:21:32,831 --> 00:21:36,231
Consort Shu used to be the carefree Princess Bi Luo of Nanlang.

264
00:21:36,231 --> 00:21:39,331
She was in love and engaged with General Kongshan in secret.

265
00:21:39,331 --> 00:21:41,111
It could have been a beautiful story.

266
00:21:41,111 --> 00:21:46,590
Yet her father, King of Nanlang, forced her to marry the late emperor of Great Cang.

267
00:21:46,590 --> 00:21:48,791
Princess Bi Luo wouldn't comply.

268
00:21:48,791 --> 00:21:51,390
In a rage, the King of Nanlang killed General Kongshan

269
00:21:51,390 --> 00:21:54,250
and threatened to kill his entire clan.

270
00:21:54,250 --> 00:21:58,091
Bi Luo had no choice but to bribe the eunuch to avoid the inspection

271
00:21:58,091 --> 00:22:00,651
and became who we knew as Consort Shu.

272
00:22:00,651 --> 00:22:06,231
Thus, she lost her love and her name.

273
00:22:06,231 --> 00:22:09,871
She stayed alive for the sake of General Kongshan's clan,

274
00:22:09,871 --> 00:22:14,151
and because she was pregnant with General Kongshan's child.

275
00:22:25,070 --> 00:22:29,271
It can't be true. No way.

276
00:22:29,271 --> 00:22:31,591
My mother consort wouldn't lie to me.

277
00:22:31,591 --> 00:22:36,371
I am a descendant of the Xiao family, a prince of the late emperor of Great Cang!

278
00:22:36,371 --> 00:22:40,431
Back then, one of those who escorted Princess Bi Luo to Great Cang

279
00:22:40,431 --> 00:22:43,771
noticed that she was unwell and discovered the truth.

280
00:22:43,771 --> 00:22:48,371
That person was attacked by assassins but made it out alive.

281
00:22:48,371 --> 00:22:52,431
Lai Luozhi, you are not a descendant of the Xiao family.

282
00:22:58,510 --> 00:23:05,051
Lai Luozhi, your life is a complete lie.

283
00:23:18,330 --> 00:23:19,830
No way.

284
00:23:20,670 --> 00:23:22,410
My mother consort wouldn't lie to me.

285
00:23:22,411 --> 00:23:24,551
My mother consort wouldn't lie to me!

286
00:23:24,551 --> 00:23:28,051
You petty people are Zhou Xu's lackeys.

287
00:23:28,051 --> 00:23:30,251
You fabricate lies to deceive everyone,

288
00:23:30,251 --> 00:23:34,951
just to prevent me from ascending the throne and rectifying the mistake.

289
00:23:50,470 --> 00:23:53,451
The moths flying to the flame,

290
00:23:53,451 --> 00:23:55,951
born at dawn,

291
00:23:55,951 --> 00:23:58,391
dead by dusk.

292
00:24:39,230 --> 00:24:41,100
It turns out...

293
00:24:42,450 --> 00:24:45,751
