You came for the Shen familyâ€”

324
00:27:19,091 --> 00:27:20,950
Director Yan,

325
00:27:21,630 --> 00:27:23,392
speak cautiously.

326
00:27:25,270 --> 00:27:28,931
Now that we are divorced, you have no ties with the Shen family.

327
00:27:28,931 --> 00:27:31,891
So stay out of my family business.

328
00:27:37,710 --> 00:27:39,380
Fine.

329
00:27:40,730 --> 00:27:42,890
Even if I am not a member of the Shen family,

330
00:27:42,890 --> 00:27:45,450
I will see this matter to its end.

331
00:27:45,451 --> 00:27:50,271
I'm not standing here as your wife

332
00:27:50,271 --> 00:27:52,891
but as the Chief Director of the Ministry of Justice.

333
00:27:52,891 --> 00:27:55,670
It's my pursuit to reinvestigate wrongful cases

334
00:27:55,670 --> 00:27:58,470
and bring justice to the innocent.

335
00:28:03,030 --> 00:28:07,211
Great Chief Shen, the Grand Empress Dowager summons you.

336
00:28:09,250 --> 00:28:11,951
As an official, you should know very well that

337
00:28:11,951 --> 00:28:14,140
the Grand Empress Dowager only summoned me, the leader.

338
00:28:14,140 --> 00:28:17,070
How can you come here without an invitation?

339
00:28:17,770 --> 00:28:20,391
Are you breaking into the hall?

340
00:28:21,270 --> 00:28:26,031
If you go in there alone, I won't see you again.

341
00:29:02,470 --> 00:29:05,651
His Majesty caught a mild cold.

342
00:29:05,651 --> 00:29:09,951
He will rest for a day and attend the court meeting tomorrow.

343
00:29:09,951 --> 00:29:15,051
My ministers, do you have any reports to make?

344
00:29:20,030 --> 00:29:24,211
Qiao Wenzhi, you're temporarily in charge of Gannandao.

345
00:29:24,211 --> 00:29:28,271
Do you have matters to report today?

346
00:29:28,271 --> 00:29:32,531
Reporting to Grand Empress Dowager. Ever since Lai Luozhi was convicted,

347
00:29:32,531 --> 00:29:35,471
all has been well and prosperous in Great Cang.

348
00:29:35,471 --> 00:29:37,911
Gannandao has been thriving.

349
00:29:37,911 --> 00:29:42,331
The world is at peace. There is nothing to report.

350
00:29:42,331 --> 00:29:44,951
"The world is at peace"?

351
00:29:44,951 --> 00:29:47,991
Lai Luozhi has been brought to justice.

352
00:29:47,991 --> 00:29:53,191
But the brochure he left behind was very useful.

353
00:29:54,270 --> 00:29:58,851
Qiao Wenzhi, you illegally imported goods from Xichen

354
00:29:58,851 --> 00:30:04,211
through Gannandao to sell them in Great Cang for profit.

355
00:30:05,450 --> 00:30:07,431
Grand Empress Dowager, I have been wronged.

356
00:30:07,431 --> 00:30:10,391
The so-called evidence left behind by those rebels

357
00:30:10,391 --> 00:30:12,491
in Gannandao is absolutely invalid.

358
00:30:12,491 --> 00:30:14,731
Absolutely invalid?

359
00:30:20,850 --> 00:30:26,231
Then, what do you say about the fabricated ledgers?

360
00:30:27,310 --> 00:30:30,871
It wasn't submitted by Lai Luozhi's people.

361
00:30:30,871 --> 00:30:35,591
The forged ledger documented twice the real cost

362
00:30:35,591 --> 00:30:38,591
of the reconstruction of Ming Hall.

363
00:30:39,910 --> 00:30:42,531
But all the ministries were involved in this.

364
00:30:42,531 --> 00:30:45,060
-  I'm not the only oneâ€” 
 - Qiao Wenzhi.

365
00:30:46,370 --> 00:30:49,751
Don't talk nonsense! Don't talk nonsense!

366
00:30:53,190 --> 00:30:58,611
Grand Empress Dowager, Qiao Wenzhi is my subordinate.

367
00:30:58,611 --> 00:31:01,670
He embezzled the money from the court out of greed,

368
00:31:01,670 --> 00:31:03,750
which is a serious crime.

369
00:31:03,751 --> 00:31:07,211
I was negligent.

370
00:31:07,211 --> 00:31:10,051
I deserve any punishment.

371
00:31:10,051 --> 00:31:12,300
Negligent?

372
00:31:13,111 --> 00:31:15,391
Prime Minister Zhang truly has a wealth of knowledge.

373
00:31:15,391 --> 00:31:17,351
What an exquisite choice of words.

374
00:31:17,351 --> 00:31:21,931
But Qiao Wenzhi is indeed loyal to you.

375
00:31:21,931 --> 00:31:25,411
I bet most of the embezzlement ended up

376
00:31:25,411 --> 00:31:28,191
in your pocket, Zhang Xingwei.

377
00:31:29,670 --> 00:31:33,811
Zhang Xingwei, what else do you have to say?

378
00:31:35,970 --> 00:31:39,691
I have nothing to say.

379
00:31:39,691 --> 00:31:41,744
Prince Xian.

380
00:31:42,990 --> 00:31:44,391
Mother Empress.

381
00:31:44,391 --> 00:31:46,511
Let me ask you.

382
00:31:46,511 --> 00:31:49,591
How should we deal with him?

383
00:31:49,591 --> 00:31:52,291
Mother Empress is wise, I believe you have your opinion.

384
00:31:52,291 --> 00:31:54,471
I have my opinion?

385
00:31:54,471 --> 00:31:59,391
But now I am asking for your opinion.

386
00:32:00,070 --> 00:32:02,231
Prime Minister Zhang has been my mentor since I was young.

387
00:32:02,231 --> 00:32:07,131
He has always led by example and taught me to prioritize the nation.

388
00:32:07,131 --> 00:32:11,251
I don't believe that he would commit such a crime just for money.

389
00:32:11,251 --> 00:32:15,271
There must be something behind this.

390
00:32:17,650 --> 00:32:21,471
Prince Xian, how foolish!

391
00:32:21,471 --> 00:32:26,311
I have deceived you for years, acting like a decent minister.

392
00:32:26,311 --> 00:32:29,751
Yet you still plead for me?

393
00:32:33,690 --> 00:32:37,871
Very well. What a touching bond between mentor and disciple.

394
00:32:37,871 --> 00:32:41,711
Prime Minister Zhang, let me speak on your behalf.

395
00:32:41,711 --> 00:32:45,671
You didn't spend a single dime on yourself.

396
00:32:45,671 --> 00:32:48,491
You bribed others in the court

397
00:32:48,491 --> 00:32:53,671
so that they supported Prince Xian with you.

398
00:33:04,700 --> 00:33:06,600
Grand Empress Dowager.

399
00:33:07,200 --> 00:33:09,000
At this point,

400
00:33:09,000 --> 00:33:13,100
I will no longer conceal the truth.

401
00:33:13,800 --> 00:33:20,600
Prince Xian knows absolutely nothing about all this.

402
00:33:21,991 --> 00:33:24,600
It was all my doing alone.

403
00:33:24,600 --> 00:33:29,400
Please sentence me to death as a warning to others.

404
00:33:29,400 --> 00:33:31,300
Do you think your sins will be erased

405
00:33:31,300 --> 00:33:34,600
as long as you sacrifice yourself?

406
00:33:37,100 --> 00:33:39,600
Those loyal officials who died wrongfully accused

407
00:33:39,600 --> 00:33:42,500
because of you

408
00:33:42,500 --> 00:33:47,600
can never be brought back to life.

409
00:33:53,400 --> 00:33:57,000
Minister Shen, bring it up.

410
00:34:06,911 --> 00:34:10,231
 By heavenly decree, here comes the edict. 

411
00:34:10,231 --> 00:34:15,000
 The criminal, Shen Bingzhu, secretly corresponded with the enemy, 

412
00:34:15,000 --> 00:34:17,500
 burned down our army's granary, 

413
00:34:17,500 --> 00:34:20,300
 leaked the weapon designs, 

414
00:34:20,300 --> 00:34:22,200
 colluded with foreign forces, 

415
00:34:22,200 --> 00:34:24,300
 and conspired with the rebel army. 

416
00:34:24,300 --> 00:34:26,500
 He shall be sentenced to death. 

417
00:34:26,500 --> 00:34:29,700
 The entire Shen family shall be detained and exiled. 

418
00:34:29,700 --> 00:34:33,500
 Convey the edict widely. 

419
00:34:34,100 --> 00:34:37,600
 I do not seek to be renowned. 

420
00:34:37,600 --> 00:34:39,800
 I only seek to have a clear conscience 

421
00:34:39,800 --> 00:34:42,100
 and not let the people down. 

422
00:34:42,100 --> 00:34:44,400
 Shen Bingzhu was indifferent to wealth and fame, 

423
00:34:44,400 --> 00:34:46,400
 never wanting to get involved in court disputes. 

424
00:34:46,400 --> 00:34:48,100
 All he cared about was the people. 

425
00:34:48,100 --> 00:34:50,000
 No matter what happened, 

426
00:34:50,000 --> 00:34:51,900
 he only did what he should do, 

427
00:34:51,900 --> 00:34:53,800
 as long as the people lived well. 

428
00:34:53,800 --> 00:34:55,800
 I receive my wage from His Majesty. 

429
00:34:55,800 --> 00:34:58,100
 Naturally, I shall share his burden 

430
00:34:58,100 --> 00:35:00,500
 even at the cost of my life. 

