00:35:09,910 --> 00:35:12,500
am here to seek justice for my father,

434
00:35:13,700 --> 00:35:15,000
Shen Bingzhu.

435
00:35:15,000 --> 00:35:18,500
 I, Shen Du, the son of the criminal official Shen Bingzhu, 

