00:36:06,200 --> 00:36:12,300
Sixteen years ago when Great Cang was at war with Xichen

446
00:36:12,300 --> 00:36:15,300
and in dire need of provisions and fodder,

447
00:36:15,300 --> 00:36:18,200
the main granary

448
00:36:18,200 --> 00:36:23,700
that stored the provisions suddenly caught fire.

449
00:36:23,700 --> 00:36:28,200
All the provisions of Great Cang were burned to the ground.

450
00:36:28,200 --> 00:36:30,700
Shen Bingzhu, who was guarding the provisions,

451
00:36:30,700 --> 00:36:33,400
was found guilty of conspiring with the enemy

452
00:36:33,400 --> 00:36:35,800
and severely punished.

453
00:36:45,500 --> 00:36:50,600
The grain bag bearing the granary's seal

454
00:36:50,600 --> 00:36:55,800
should have been burned to ashes.

455
00:36:56,751 --> 00:36:58,791
But it appeared...

456
00:37:00,000 --> 00:37:04,100
a thousand miles away in Gannandao.

457
00:37:06,400 --> 00:37:09,800
The traitorous letter you presented to the late emperor

458
00:37:09,800 --> 00:37:14,300
was found not to have been written by Shen Bingzhu.

459
00:37:15,100 --> 00:37:20,000
Prime Minister Zhang, will you explain it to me?

460
00:37:20,000 --> 00:37:23,800
When the war began, my disciple came to me.

461
00:37:23,800 --> 00:37:25,400
It was then I learned

462
00:37:25,400 --> 00:37:29,900
that he had colluded with local officials to scalp the provisions.

463
00:37:29,900 --> 00:37:31,600
They bought the provisions at a low price

464
00:37:31,600 --> 00:37:35,500
and sold them when the price rose to profit from the price difference.

465
00:37:35,500 --> 00:37:39,800
However, the war with Xichen broke out.

466
00:37:39,800 --> 00:37:42,500
But they had sold out all the provisions,

467
00:37:42,500 --> 00:37:46,000
leaving only piles of thatch in the granary.

468
00:37:51,551 --> 00:37:53,991
Prime Minister Zhang.

469
00:37:53,991 --> 00:37:57,791
It had never crossed my mind that

470
00:37:57,800 --> 00:38:01,800
such a heinous crime concerning the foundation of Great Cang

471
00:38:01,800 --> 00:38:05,400
would have something to do with you.

472
00:38:05,400 --> 00:38:08,000
Grand Empress Dowager.

473
00:38:08,000 --> 00:38:11,600
Nor had I imagined that...

474
00:38:13,100 --> 00:38:19,000
