478
00:38:38,000 --> 00:38:43,300
imitating Minister Shen's handwriting.

479
00:38:43,300 --> 00:38:45,800
You forged the letter.

480
00:38:45,800 --> 00:38:50,000
Then, how did the granary catch fire?

481
00:38:50,600 --> 00:38:52,200
Prime Minister Zhang.

482
00:38:53,791 --> 00:38:57,151
