490
00:39:25,400 --> 00:39:27,800
Protect someone important?

491
00:39:29,231 --> 00:39:32,711
Who are you referring to?

492
00:39:37,800 --> 00:39:44,900
There are things I can't speak about openly.

493
00:39:51,071 --> 00:39:53,431
 Great Chief Shen, please. 

494
00:40:17,700 --> 00:40:19,900
 Do you trust me so much? 

495
00:40:19,900 --> 00:40:22,000
 Aren't you afraid 

496
00:40:22,000 --> 00:40:26,900
 that you will disappear along with this box? 

497
00:40:26,900 --> 00:40:28,200
 Over the years, 

498
00:40:28,200 --> 00:40:32,400
 I have seen you serving the people of Great Cang at all costs. 

499
00:40:32,400 --> 00:40:35,600
 I believe you will make a fair judgment. 

500
00:40:35,600 --> 00:40:37,600
 I am not afraid... 

501
00:40:38,991 --> 00:40:41,351
 to risk my life. 

502
00:40:54,000 --> 00:40:58,900
Then let me speak on your behalf.

503
00:40:59,591 --> 00:41:03,591
Before Minister Shen took over the granary,

504
